*Znao* je da će se sve ovo dogoditi. (He knew that all this would happen.)

*Znao* sam da neću uspeti. (I knew I wouldn't succeed.)

*Znala* je da je to bilo nemoguće. (She knew that it was impossible.)

*Znali* smo da je to nemoguće. (We knew it was impossible.)

*Znaš* li kako da to uradiš? (Do you know how to do that?)

*Znaće* li on kako da to uradi? (Will he know how to do that?)